data.description: This modern single story home features an oversized corner lot and custom upgrades that are rare to find in an urban home!  You will love the open floor plan with modern wood-like flooring and stunning contemporary lighting throughout the home. The kitchen boasts beautiful granite countertops, oversized custom cabinetry, newer stainless steel appliances, an oversized stainless steel sink and custom lighting throughout. The primary suite is in the back of the home and showcases views of the spacious backyard. A spa-like primary ensuite bathroom boasts a large walk-in closet, a luxurious tiled shower, and a contemporary vanity with a custom LED backlit mirror. Two spacious bedrooms in the front of the home have generous closets, tall 8-foot doors, plush carpet and easy access to the stunning secondary bathroom. There is also an indoor utility room with brilliant decorative tile and plenty of storage. The backyard offers plenty of space to customize your oasis and a side-entry gate with private parking for two vehicles.  946 Canton was built in 2021 and offers a low maintenance lifestyle with an outstanding  location - only minutes away from Spurs games at the Frost Bank Center and all of Downtown San Antonio's best attractions!
